    "Key to this is the development of methods for efficient data handling, which minimizes data redundancy and optimizes data usage across multiple nodes during the training process.",
    "B. Communication Challenges facing FedFMThrough revealing the inherent complexity of FMs, combined with the distributed nature of FL, we identify the following key communication challenges facing FedFM.",
